{"tid":1693571,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"就嚟五個月喇唔該 頂你個肺","createTime":"2019-11-04T16:22:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T17:19:19.000Z","uid":312736,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0436f8c55935215192c010dd5df868952f350f73","tid":1693571,"uid":312736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:22:39.000Z","msg":"呢場運動就嚟五個月喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n死咗好多人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n周同學墜樓到依家都唔知醒唔醒到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁多位香港人 <br />\n已經有咁多位手足作出犧牲<br />\n我哋呢啲仲未有事嘅係咪應該要出返淡氣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至少聽日戴個口罩呀<br />\n唔好忘記佢哋喇<br />\n佢哋連命都交上 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">乜我哋連戴一個殺傷力都冇嘅口罩都唔肯咩？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"33acf7d784a6c782704f8595cee0036bbcbf3d69","tid":1693571,"uid":312736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:23:17.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff0c32c554f6f016b28aadf133a7e4cbf56958e","tid":1693571,"uid":312736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:23:27.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"830f81c264e2be354960b2602be871bdde322e2d","tid":1693571,"uid":312736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:23:57.000Z","msg":"推呀屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a0577ed310bb48e4f4f7638caa8ce92762b2e8","tid":1693571,"uid":259400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:24:19.000Z","msg":"P牌推乜9"},{"pid":"9a8e4b7ffb9a1dfb72f38182f33e18bfff4b020c","tid":1693571,"uid":312736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:24:19.000Z","msg":"推呀頂你個肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hk